o:ExtendedAttributeTargetItem.a:Name: mdde_ExampleDataType
o:ExtendedAttributeTargetItem.a:Comment: Whether the example data is a source input or expected output.
o:ExtendedAttributeTargetItem.a:GetMethodScript: Function %Get%(obj) Dim objExampleEntity : Set objExampleEntity = obj.GetExtendedAttribute("mdde_ExampleEntity") If Not(objExampleEntity Is Nothing) Then If obj.GetExtendedAttribute("mdde_ExampleEntity") = obj.ParentObject.GetExtendedAttribute("mdde_ExampleEntity") Then %Get% = "Expected output" Else %Get% = "Source input" End If Else %Get% = "" End If End Function
o:ExtendedAttributeTargetItem.a:Label: Example data type (MDDE)
